  "texts": [
    "To address this, we incorporated an action recommender, a RL-based model.",
    "The model scores all valid actions available to the player in each round, allowing the LLM agent to focus on the top k highest score actions.",
    "We use the learned embedding from Danzero (Lu et al., 2023) to score every valid action.",
    "This part refers to step 3 in Figure 2.",
    "After transforming game states and history into a readable format and getting the top k actions selected by the action recommender, we design prompts to guide Preprint LLMs to find the best ways to play the game."
  ],
